summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 45W page 118 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Lots 1-14 incl., Block 3, Lots 1-16 incl., Block 4, Lots 1-10 incl., Block 8, all in Rainier Blvd. Add., located on the west side of Hiawatha Pl., from Dearborn St. to M zone boundary south of Judkings St., from Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone to Manufacturing (M) Zone.
